novasearch (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Rust-based indexing daemon with inotify filesystem monitoring
  * GTK3 search panel plugin for XFCE4
  * SQLite database backend for fast search
  * Configurable include/exclude patterns
  * Global keyboard shortcut support
  * Systemd user service integration

 -- NovaSearch Team <novasearch@example.com>  Sat, 07 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000
